name: Delicious Lakkaberry Krumkakes
desc: A classic dessert from Nod-Krai. The crispy egg rolls break apart in the mouth with a heavenly crackle, contrasting with the smooth, sweet filling inside. A juxtaposition of textures that come together in perfect harmony on the palate. Before the taste has had time to linger, the hand has already reached for another bite.

value.text: Increases all party members' Shield Strength by 30% for 300s. In Co-Op Mode, this effect only applies to your own character(s).
